Racing Club won the championship on 23 Nov with the following line ups:

Boca Juniors: Claudio Vacca; José Manuel Marante, Francisco Perroncino; 
              Carlos Adolfo Sosa, Salvador Grecco, Natalio Agustín Pescia; 
              Alfredo Martínez, Delfín Edmundo Benítez, Juan José Ferraro,
              Francisco Campana, Marcos Busico. 

Racing Club:  Antonio Oscar Rodríguez; Higinio García, Nicolás Palma; 
              Juan Carlos Fonda, Alberto Inocencio Rastelli, Ernesto Gutiérrez;
              Juan Carlos Salvini, Norberto Doroteo Méndez, Rubén Norberto Bravo,
              Llamil Simes, Ezra Sued. Coach: Guillermo Stábile.

Referee:      Richard H. Maddison.

Field:        Boca Juniors.

Att.:         25.000.

